                <span class="">Jacob Oleiski</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="oleiskiJ" start="1206.182" end="x">. . . with the mood that prevails in Germany, and with the attitude and indifference of the German population even now towards our depredations . . . I do not see any possibility of any communication [?] between us Jews even with the progressives, even with those circles of population who have not participated in the Hitler regime.</span>
        </li>
