            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Jacob Oleiski</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="oleiskiJ" start="1419.201" end="x">Skilled workers or cultural workers, or a person needed for an important public office—only for such people can one prevail upon the director that he permit acceptance [of him] into the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>.</span>
